# Configuration Files

To declutter the explorer view following files are grouped in the Visual Studio Code Explorer view under this file.

These are controlled by this [VSCode workspace setting](vscode://settings/explorer.fileNesting.patterns)

| File          | Description                          |
|---------------|--------------------------------------|
| [.codeqlignore](.codeqlignore) | Ignored files for the GitHub CodeQL scanner. |
| [.cspell.txt](.cspell.txt) | Workspace dictionary for cspell spell checker. |
| [.envrc](.envrc) | Auto-configure script for `direnv`. |
| [.gitattributes](.gitattributes) | Defines attributes for pathnames. |
| [.gitignore](.gitignore) | Specifies files and directories to ignore in git. |
| [pyrightconfig.json](pyrightconfig.json) | Configuration for Pyright static type checker. |

## Other Explorer Groupings

### README.md

All root `*.md` files (except this file, CONFIG.md) are grouped under [README.md](README.md), so they are all found in one place.

### [docs/README.md](docs/README.md)

Groups all the markdown files in the docs/ directory

### Mermaid Diagrams

The output from Mermaid diagrams are folded under the Mermaid `.mmd` file